      </li>
      <li>
        He dropped the ring and lost it to the centipede demon, living his days in agony
      </li>
      <li>
        Protects his sister Quelana's grave, caring only for family
      </li>
      <li>
        Chases you to his death should you dishonor his sister's grave and try to run away
      </li>
